buildPhases.name: [CP] Check Pods Manifest.lock
buildPhases.shellScript:
diff "${PODS_PODFILE_DIR_PATH}/Podfile.lock" "${PODS_ROOT}/Manifest.lock" > /dev/null
if [ $? != 0 ] ; then
    # print error to STDERR
    echo "error: The sandbox is not in sync with the Podfile.lock. Run 'pod install' or update your CocoaPods installation." >&2
    exit 1
fi
# This output is used by Xcode 'outputs' to avoid re-running this script phase.
echo "SUCCESS" > "${SCRIPT_OUTPUT_FILE_0}"

buildPhases.displayName: Change Bundle Display Name for enterprise
buildPhases.name: Change Bundle Display Name for enterprise
buildPhases.shellScript:
ipaname=`/usr/libexec/PlistBuddy -c "Print CFBundleDisplayName" "$CONFIGURATION_BUILD_DIR/pitaya.app/zh-Hans.lproj/InfoPlist.strings"`
version=`/usr/libexec/PlistBuddy -c "Print CFBundleVersion" "$CONFIGURATION_BUILD_DIR/pitaya.app/info.plist"`
ipabundleid=`/usr/libexec/PlistBuddy -c "Print CFBundleIdentifier" "$CONFIGURATION_BUILD_DIR/pitaya.app/info.plist"`

ipaname="小鹿陪玩内测"
echo "version:${version} ipaname:${ipaname} bundleid:${ipabundleid}"

enterprisebundleid="com.aaron.enterprise.pitaya"
distributionbundleid="com.aaron.pitaya"

if [ "$ipabundleid"x = "$enterprisebundleid"x ]; then
/usr/libexec/PlistBuddy -c "Set :CFBundleDisplayName $ipaname" "$CONFIGURATION_BUILD_DIR/pitaya.app/zh-Hans.lproj/InfoPlist.strings"
elif [ "$ipabundleid"x != "$distributionbundleid"x ]; then
custombundlename=${ipabundleid##*com.aaron.pitaya.}
echo "custombundlename:${custombundlename}"
/usr/libexec/PlistBuddy -c "Set :CFBundleDisplayName $custombundlename" "$CONFIGURATION_BUILD_DIR/pitaya.app/zh-Hans.lproj/InfoPlist.strings"
else
echo "isDistrutebution"
fi

exit 0
